        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 23 at 12:14AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1214 AM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 4
miles north of Claude, moving northeast at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Claude.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
